title: Agile
content: Agile is a software development methodology that focuses on communication and feedback throughout the development process. It also emphasizes working software over comprehensive documentation, and each iteration that a team makes to its product is seen as an opportunity to perfect it. Agile continues to grow in popularity, and its focus on communication with users directly benefits digital products.
